{"title":"故乡的夜（外一首）","authors":["阎纯德"],"dates":[{"year":1995,"month":11,"day":28}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"故乡的夜（外一首）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"阎纯德"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"夜悄悄走下大山，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"用网一张"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"朦胧家乡的平原。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我的村子"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"最后熄灭小灯一盏，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"皱一下愁眉"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"闭上双眼，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"像一只晚归的耕牛，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"披一身汗水，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"回到家园；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"然后藏进寂寞，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"微笑着"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"享受自己那份温暖……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"夜鸟"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我回来了，跟着夜鸟。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"几颗星星"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"洒落得很深很远，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"几声雁叫"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"为梦魇制作符号。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"抗日枪声"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在山后写成遥远的故事，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"天河没有水，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"听不到“黄河在咆哮”；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"黄昏里掐一朵野花"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那是英雄灵魂的燃烧；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"秋虫唧唧，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"依然是太行军号。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我回来了，从山那边，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"没有星光照耀，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"处处险关险道。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"家乡鼾声不小，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"城里醉翁不倒，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"长城像一头奔跑的大象，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一声嘶鸣，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"把历史写上云霄；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我回来了，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"心跳伴着雁叫……"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":10,"page_end":10}